episodes.title: Former Prince Andrew is arrested in the wake of the Epstein files release
episodes.description:
Former Prince Andrew, now known as Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor after his title was stripped, was released from police custody on Thursday after he was arrested on suspicion of misconduct in public office.

Thames Valley Police released an updated statement confirming "a man in his sixties" was released while the investigation continues. Officials added that their searches in Norfolk had ended, but will continue in Berkshire.

Read more: https://thenationaldesk.com/news/americas-news-now/former-england-prince-andrew-mountbatten-windsor-arrested-on-misconduct-in-public-office-allegations-jeffrey-epstein-files-trade-reports
